party plugins.<\/li><li>Updated TinyMCE to resolve an issue with spacing.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Deprecated<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After the update, if you are using any deprecated functions\/hooks and environment is set to <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/faq\/how-to-set-debug-mode\/\">development <\/a>you will be able to see error notices.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also if you are using any <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/edit-view-files-without-messing-the-core-view-files\/\">my_ prefixed view files<\/a>, you should re-check them and try to upgrade any deprecated functions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Classes\/Controllers<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Admin_controller<\/strong> is deprecated if you are using your own controller in any custom files and these controllers are extending the <strong>Admin_controller <\/strong>class, instead, you should extend the <strong>AdminController<\/strong>,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Clients_controller <\/strong>is deprecated if you are using your own controller in any custom files and these controllers are extending the  <br><strong>Clients_controller <\/strong> class, instead, you should extend the <strong>ClientsController<\/strong>, <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>CRM_Controller <\/strong>and <strong>CRM_Model<\/strong> are <strong><g class=\"gr_ gr_16 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Punctuation only-del replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"16\" data-gr-id=\"16\">deprecated,<\/g><\/strong> if you are extending any of these classes you should update your code to use <strong>App_Controller <\/strong>and <strong>App_Model<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Functions<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The function <strong>format_money <\/strong>is deprecated,  use <strong>app_format_money<\/strong>($total, $currency, $excludeSymbol = false)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The function <strong>logActivity<\/strong> is deprecated, use <strong>log_activity <\/strong>($description, $staffid = null) instead<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hooks<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Action <strong>after_js_scripts_render <\/strong>is deprecated, use <strong>app_admin_footer<\/strong> instead.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Action <strong>customers_after_js_scripts_load<\/strong> is deprecated, use <strong>app_customers_footer <\/strong>instead.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Filters <strong>before_add_online_payment_modes <\/strong>and <strong>before_add_payment_gateways <\/strong>are deprecated, use <strong>app_payment_gateways<\/strong> instead.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Added ability to send payment receipt manually after it&#8217;s recorded. Added ability to chose lead duplicate validation check fields. Added ability to chose decimal, thousand separators and currency placement per currency. Added Paypal New Smart Checkout implementation. Improved invoice, estimate, subscription HTML views to be more similar like contracts and proposal. Added deprecation warnings on [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[23],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4111","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-changelog"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4111","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4111"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4111\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4111"}],"wp:term":[{"taxon